{"tid":2070777,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東方報業去年轉虧蝕逾千萬元　不派末期息","createTime":"2020-06-19T10:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:41:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a7dddc359f1a32cc7865bfaa1ee85948199dff","tid":2070777,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"東方報業（0018）公布，截至今年3月底止年度，集團由盈轉虧，蝕1098.7萬元，去年同期嫌賺8138.8萬元，每股虧損0.46仙，不派末期息，去年派每股2仙。<br />\n<br />\n集團錄得收入8.23億元，按年跌8.7%；綜合年度虧損1156.7萬元，按年跌1.14倍，主要由於印刷媒體業務收入減少，香港及澳洲的投資物業損失所致。若剔除投資物業公允價值的變動及澳元匯兌損失的影響，集團來自主要業務的年度溢利為7175.3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n集團指，董事會明白印刷 媒體在廣告市場的佔有率逐漸被蠶食，而發行量亦逐年遞減，此乃客觀事實。為化解困局，集團的營運策略須更靈活，包括報章內容和廣告價格都要具競爭力，為客戶提供更彈性的宣傳 組合及與新商品開展合作機會等等。另一方面要為消費市場迅速復甦作準備，盡快回復集團的收入增長。<br />\n<br />\n東方報收報0.45元，跌1.09%。"},{"pid":"bbc11c08f48c80c6d8089001e98e498fbbb3fa2f","tid":2070777,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592563520418&amp;issue=20200619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592563520418%26issue%3D20200619&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C94mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=87330354\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592563520418%26issue%3D20200619&h=31014f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592563520418&amp;issue=20200619</a>"},{"pid":"0afbc8ac4332dd6cbd43ce542e618448ee485cef","tid":2070777,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6af7d60ed0bd91e64ace09131c3b9ab0d13115c","tid":2070777,"uid":129243